      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? This beauty has been so good to me and is still in great shape for its next owner. It drives super smooth, the interior is nice and comfy, and it\u2019s just been a total joy to own. It\u2019s perfect if you want something dependable without breaking the bank. Come on over and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
