      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, factory-rated at 333hp with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential Lock. This chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring long-term structural and timing integrity. The suspension maintains its composure with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, preserving the chassis's legendary neutral handling and tactile hydraulic steering feedback. While the exterior shows honest patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing clearances and valve adjustments\u2014are within spec, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking peak S54 performance.",
